servinfo.title: Air Cleaner Filter Inspection
servinfo.ptxt: Check that filter is not excessively dirty, damaged or oily and clean filter with compressed air from air outlet side of filter.
Refer to Air Cleaner Filter Inspection and Cleaning:For M16A Engine with VVT , Air Cleaner Filter Inspection and Cleaning:For J20 Engine or Air Cleaner Filter Inspection and Cleaning:For F9Q Engine .
